{"tid":500870,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[NBA] John Collins拿到兩雙 創老鷹新秀記錄","createTime":"2017-12-16T08:44:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T13:57:48.000Z","uid":106204,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fc2b825aba7f95d77bfc1a1c9bf1069ecca30c10","tid":500870,"uid":106204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T08:44:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong> John Collins拿到兩雙 創老鷹新秀記錄</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n10月23日訊 據NBA記者Mike Conti&rlm;報道，約翰-科林斯是老鷹隊自1983年以來最快獲得兩雙的新秀。<br />\n<br />\n當今天老鷹隊和籃網隊的三節比賽打完，約翰-科林斯已經得到了12分13個籃板的兩雙數據。<br />\n<br />\n2017年NBA選秀中，約翰-科林斯在首輪第19順位被老鷹隊選中。<br />\n<br />\n今年7月，約翰-科林斯代表老鷹隊參加了拉斯維加斯夏季聯賽，並入選最佳陣容第一陣容。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebccc8f780a91b9731cca1628ae2faf9ff00b3f0","tid":500870,"uid":106204,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T08:44:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60d824e5ea453a069c37b4e809577466ea68306","tid":500870,"uid":1713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T08:48:12.000Z","msg":"一線鷹無人留意架啦"},{"pid":"866eac0ae320b258a2b413fea61f4e0189e1eee9","tid":500870,"uid":106204,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T08:49:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b969293856a8e57f1078d85638387b8245fe1b6e","tid":500870,"uid":18389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T08:50:42.000Z","msg":"Let&rsquo;s go HAWKS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e51aab1519184d94b787b7eb2a628a0134b19887","tid":500870,"uid":54025,"like":0,"d